track_notes: The approach to this summit is longer than originally reported.  This route is 6.5 miles long and took over 3 hours moving at a moderate pace.
Shortest route to summit via an off trail scramble up the ridge.
track_title: Shorter Descent Route via direct scramble back to trail

track_notes: This is probably the quickest route to the AZ for Proffit.  Note at approximately 37.56678, -90.79342 you want to turn off the trail, hike up hill and find the jeep trail.  This jeep trail will lead you directly to the AZ, and is easy going.
